examples.en: The zebra is a black-and-white striped animal.
Other guests sat under similarly striped umbrellas.
Striped tails are a common feature of many animals.
A striped dress was prefaced by an ample apron.
The children carefully striped the paper with red and blue paint.
Dad brought back his prize catch, a three-foot striped bass.
Stripe is an apt name for the cat, since she has striped fur.
